{"tid":1180644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"崩潰！舌戰《FOX》美女主播 劉欣被懷疑有雙重國籍","createTime":"2019-06-01T04:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T15:30:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":625,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3e291fe1302433da21966ff301254c3d9a5f14","tid":1180644,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpL3hKmY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpL3hKmY.jpg&h=56b61492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國官媒央視旗下英語頻道《中國環球電視網》（CGTN）主播劉欣，5月30日與美國《福斯財經新聞網》主播黎根（Trish Regan）辯論貿易戰話題；中國網友翻牆發現劉竟為美國籍，且丈夫、孩子也擁外國國籍，他們對此感到崩潰與氣憤。<br />\n<br />\n中國網友發現，劉欣雖在中國「百度百科」的個人資料中，標註國籍為中國，但在牆外的維基百科卻註明劉有「美國」國籍，且劉除了微博以外，也還有使用推特、臉書等被中國政府禁用的社群媒體；目前劉欣在維基百科的資料已遭人修改，「國籍」資料被移除。<br />\n<br />\n中國網友指出，劉欣在2018年10月6日，曾在個人微博「劉欣CGTN」帳號中PO出照片與短短1行文字，當中顯示她站在希臘岸邊，遙望著蔚藍海洋的另一頭，她指出，「愛琴海邊，對岸是我孩子的故鄉土耳其」；中國網友對此認為她的丈夫、孩子都並非只擁有中國國籍。<br />\n<br />\n事件在中國社群媒體「微博」愈演愈烈，同時搜尋「劉欣」、「國籍」2組關鍵字可見大量中國網友的討論串，他們表示「兩軍交戰怎麼站隊？讓人怎麼信任」、「學了個新詞：離岸愛國主義」、「她不是中國籍」、「她老公是土耳其裔的德國人，她有一個混血兒子和一個混血女兒」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php9lddce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php9lddce.jpg&h=116e4942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國網友發現，劉欣在維基百科的國籍掛著美國籍，百度百科顯示的是中國籍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpFlXTrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpFlXTrV.jpg&h=7690b9bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉欣在2018年10月6日貼出在愛琴海邊的照片，並指出土耳其是她孩子的故鄉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2808768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2808768&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=63ee427f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2808768&h=d95b3404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2808768</a>"},{"pid":"2eaadb344150335d86fcf5f9378b77bdcce583e8","tid":1180644,"uid":51436,"like":601,"dislike":2,"score":599,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:04:09.000Z","msg":"大陸狗既㭍法可以話係層出不窮"},{"pid":"c4a276725c37f8971f94bf70dacd3a3dfbe6d0b5","tid":1180644,"uid":31637,"like":281,"dislike":4,"score":277,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:04:25.000Z","msg":"返返去中國個老母閪度啦, 咁撚多國籍托咩"},{"pid":"2f6331df655ae86fef1c1f666d73b4063f93df98","tid":1180644,"uid":48083,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:07:40.000Z","msg":"依家係中國<br />\n論戰嗰排係冇國籍<br />\n之前唔知，好似有改動過<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=刘欣_(主持人)&amp;action=history\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fw%2Findex.php%3Ftitle%3D%E5%88%98%E6%AC%A3_%28%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E4%BA%BA%29%26action%3Dhistory&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=91f1435f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=刘欣_(主持人)&amp;action=history</a>"},{"pid":"5e354a4199bca25523f8eb951d9bc1fed405e4ca","tid":1180644,"uid":56063,"like":346,"dislike":0,"score":346,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"點解佢哋個個影相啲pose咁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d486fde742659740f3b808642c110644233657a","tid":1180644,"uid":8171,"like":188,"dislike":2,"score":186,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"自己嘅背景咁尷尬就咪衝出嚟柒啦，舌戰時啲理據又牽強，收皮啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27f656629b60e1274cc578a20a8d6f2e5259006","tid":1180644,"uid":35430,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"出得去幫共狗消毒嘅冇外國護照先出奇"},{"pid":"826d93fdb984433558dc73967b2e33a1a3b676c3","tid":1180644,"u